{"tid":2030581,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"從大數據分析香港被支那摧毀事件","createTime":"2020-05-22T23:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T06:01:32.000Z","uid":88982,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1844f743306dcb36c0eadfef1ba696ed5d622b0e","tid":2030581,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:50:46.000Z","msg":"大家好 由早幾日開始 全香港都好關注香港未來<br />\n但係反觀世界 除左政治家外 到底有幾多人留意事態既發展呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/trendingsearches/daily?geo=GB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrends.google.com%2Ftrends%2Ftrendingsearches%2Fdaily%3Fgeo%3DGB&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=af24d95c\" target=\"_blank\">https://trends.google.com/trends/trendingsearches/daily?geo=GB</a><br />\n由google 既搜尋器顯示 就岩岩22/5 有2萬次以上既搜尋<br />\n單日計排第12 <br />\n而國家層面上最撐我地既美國反而無入榜<br />\n值得一提既左膠大國德國反而都有排第20 -1萬次以上既搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/trendingsearches/daily?geo=DE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrends.google.com%2Ftrends%2Ftrendingsearches%2Fdaily%3Fgeo%3DDE&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=e26c34f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://trends.google.com/trends/trendingsearches/daily?geo=DE</a><br />\n由以上資料顯示<br />\n唔計美國 <br />\n英國 同 德國 係我地既重心<br />\n因為我諗大家都知道西方世界政府既取態好睇民意<br />\n所以Twitter 戰線真係好重要既戰場<br />\n求下大家除左自己之外 仲叫埋身邊未裝Twitter 既人一齊join<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>然後用 #hong kong security law 既 hashtag</strong></span><br />\n不斷like/ retweet le個topic 既post<br />\n可能你會覺得無用 哂時間 on9等等<br />\n但請相信我地香港人既力量<br />\n滴水能穿石 <br />\n我地而家身處2020年 為左我地既未來 我地既下一代 <br />\n亦為左一班停留左係2019年 犧牲左既手足 而奮戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命 寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3cb3f0e2d025bf87c201e95f30079900eb5433ad","tid":2030581,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c3a248b24f388be9cf573531f1022528bb30ee","tid":2030581,"uid":10150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19ff79a9b63f8f48653f2a24b7a810b01b2615a","tid":2030581,"uid":88982,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:55:48.000Z","msg":"講多少少 小弟因為之前工作關係<br />\n都認識一班so-called 唔同階層既精英份子<br />\n佢地之前一直淨係識搵錢 咩都唔關佢地事<br />\nle期佢地雖然未去到即刻要移民既階段<br />\n但係已經盡量將手頭上既資產換返Cash<br />\n佢地好明白今次係比反送中嚴重好撚多"},{"pid":"79ce01863697fcc1c2d675198ec03dc72b934843","tid":2030581,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:58:31.000Z","msg":"推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9585caaf3203298d090987030a11f11a9cea84b9","tid":2030581,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:59:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feee746bc2e478d123c86e3c3bc00fdb86b4d972","tid":2030581,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T00:02:18.000Z","msg":"為左方便大家 我搵埋d link<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LindseyGrahamSC/status/1263623930696339457?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLindseyGrahamSC%2Fstatus%2F1263623930696339457%3Fs%3D20&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=62cbe561\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLindseyGrahamSC%2Fstatus%2F1263623930696339457%3Fs%3D20&h=484a75a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LindseyGrahamSC/status/1263623930696339457?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorRomney/status/1263832316058701824?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorRomney%2Fstatus%2F1263832316058701824%3Fs%3D20&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=6627b6d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?